products.title: Turin 25mm Coral Pink Perfect Fit Venetian Blind
products.description: This 25mm coral orange venetian blind adds a saturated shade of orange to your room. Beautiful when paired with natural and wooden tones throughout the home. The perfect fit aspect of this blind means it fits straight onto upvc frames with no need for screws or drills. Product id: db-dpfven0361 fabric colour: coral pink s25138 material: aluminium headrail: minimal perfect fit framework - easy drill-free installation clip slat width: 25mm control type: tilt wand, tensioned cord-free raise.
